This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with reinforcement learning algorithms. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as RL is a subfield of AI. Additionally, the paper discusses the application of these algorithms to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY), which are related fields. Finally, the paper deals with safety constraints, which could also place it in the sub-category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
